{"tid":1451760,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[以眼還眼] 推到聽日全港18區都有放映","createTime":"2019-08-11T20:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T03:34:00.000Z","uid":294095,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8f66ab64c566c77789edb7a083159368f24b828a","tid":1451760,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:29:36.000Z","msg":"🎥🎥<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>18區連儂放映會- 全港集結</strong></span></span>🎥🎥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OUQtdZk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOUQtdZk.png&h=707f9fbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n811激起民憤，無奈只停留左喺同溫層<br />\n我地要令更多人知道TVB以外既真相<br />\n(雖然今次TVB都助攻)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點幫手?</strong></span></span><br />\n有放映裝備就可以揀個地方播，Pro既可以係Projector/電視，再平民啲可以一部tablet 都得<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ipQ5gbK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FipQ5gbK.jpg&h=067b2198&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yddyp49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyddyp49.jpg&h=6ee02f04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>喺邊道搵片? 同埋點下載?</strong></span></span><br />\n以下有個呢道有個DataBase，儲起左811既片段，同埋其他相關既片段<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2H1p3ix\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2H1p3ix&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=7fc634bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2H1p3ix</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>冇時間放映? </strong></span></span><br />\n可以贊助我地擴大放映會<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/18區連儂放映會基金/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F18%E5%8D%80%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E6%94%BE%E6%98%A0%E6%9C%83%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%2F&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=299219f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/18區連儂放映會基金/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n獲得最新18區連儂放映資訊:<br />\nFacebook Group: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/fb18districts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Ffb18districts&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=e93a9186\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/fb18districts</a><br />\nTG Group: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/18districts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F18districts&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=ff3dd33f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/18districts</a>"},{"pid":"4a57bf09c4c126d2d2fa352e4b9a1ee40b727c89","tid":1451760,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:29:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66a12228024d0370cab48f439be3f54295cbec1","tid":1451760,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:33:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca245c15f821ba6266d0f72da6f4ccaa62469a5","tid":1451760,"uid":207476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:34:37.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">[url]仲有良知嘅你可唔可以幫手Send個Email去國際刑事法院 控告香港警察<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449403</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]</span></span>"},{"pid":"75a74a8a14d3a81a4aaa4b190ab88e64f43d212c","tid":1451760,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:36:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f